            "last_activity_date": 1498570624,
            "creation_date": 1476268336,
            "body": "<p>You're on your way<\/p>\n\n<p>\"!= true\"  = false; <\/p>\n\n<p>\"!= false\" = true<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>(a) b == true\n    if (b)\n(b) b == false\n    if (!b)\n(c) b != true\n    if (!b)\n(d) b != false\n    if (b)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>EDIT: Three answers, all the same and correct. I don't know why one user downvoted them all. The answerer can't help noob-questions being asked here.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 39996415,
            "question_id": 39996347,
