            "creation_date": 1476268486,
            "body": "<pre><code>a) if(b)\nb) if(!b)\nc) if(!b)\nd) if(b) (because of double negation, not false is true)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>More info about the Java Boolean Condition Logic : <a href=\"http://codingbat.com/doc/java-if-boolean-logic.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://codingbat.com/doc/java-if-boolean-logic.html<\/a> <\/p>\n\n<p>Have a good day ;)<\/p>\n",
